lease\/\">Press release<\/a>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"entry-title\"><a href=\"\/2025\/12\/18\/dystrack-a-new-tool-for-dynamic-sample-tracking-joins-the-push-to-bring-smart-microscopy-to-everyday-imaging\/\" rel=\"bookmark\">DySTrack: A new tool for Dynamic Sample Tracking joins the push to bring smart microscopy to everyday imaging<\/a><\/h2>\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Smart microscopy promises adaptive, sample-aware imaging but has seen limited adoption in biology labs because it often requires bespoke hardware, vendor-specific solutions, or complex software frameworks. A new python-based open-source software tool, DySTrack (Dynamic Sample Tracking), now joins recent efforts to change this by making smart microscopy more accessible on standard commercial microscopes. DySTrack, developed\u2026<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"entry-meta\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<time class=\"entry-date published\" datetime=\"2025-12-18T10:18:43+01:00\">18 December 2025<\/time><time class=\"updated\" datetime=\"2025-12-18T10:18:44+01:00\">18 December 2025<\/time>\t\t\t\t<\/div><!-- .entry-meta -->\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div><!-- .entry-wrapper -->\n\t<\/article>\n\n\t\t\n\t<article data-post-id=\"3049\"\n\t\tclass=\"category-press-release type-post post-has-image\"\n\t\t\t\t>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"post-thumbnail\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"\/2025\/11\/20\/ai-agents-advance-atomic-force-microscopy-automation\/\" rel=\"bookmark\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"647\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/smartmicroscopy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/image_press_iitd.png?fit=1200%2C647&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"attachment-newspack-article-block-uncropped size-newspack-article-block-uncropped wp-post-image\" alt=\"AI agents advance atomic force microscopy automation: new benchmark reveals capabilities and critical safety concerns\" data-hero-candidate=\"1\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/smartmicroscopy.org\/wp-content\/u